org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM relations WHERE relations.from_id = "$1" AND relations.to_id IS NULL AND NOT(hierarchy + relates + duplicates + follows + blocks + includes + requires > 1) LIMIT 1

rewrites.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM relations WHERE relations.from_id = "$1" AND False AND NOT(hierarchy + relates + duplicates + follows + blocks + includes + requires > 1) LIMIT 1
